des: Where do the locals go? What do you want to do for dinner? Answer these questions with LocalStreet! LocalStreet will find unique restaurants, breweries, bars and boutiques near you. LocalStreet has been designed to work with Alexa, Google Home, Apple and Android smartphones so you can take us with you wherever you go!
